title: Duck Donuts bringing made-to-order treats to Kissimmee
text:
Griffin said the doughnut shop will serve cake donuts, retailing for about $13 for a dozen. 
“You can come in and get a dozen in about 10 minutes,” Griffin said. 
Griffin, whose background is real estate development, said he has plans to open more restaurants in Central Florida. He is next looking for leases in Winter Park and Lake Buena Vista.
